rfc2036"><span>https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2036</span></a></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td><span id="docs-internal-guid-25110c4e-af78-f42f-a663-2cb79315b715"><span><span id="docs-internal-guid-887bf9d1-af78-baf5-fdad-868fccdb62c5"><span>RFC 2050 – Internet Registry IP Allocation Guidelines</span></span></span></span></td> <td style="text-align: center;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-cfec7928-af75-0dc2-5c29-cb4ebc49de49"><span>IETF</span></span></td> <td><span id="docs-internal-guid-f76b56a8-af72-72fc-f66f-3289685e9058"><a href="https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2050"><span>https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2050</span></a></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td><span id="docs-internal-guid-187bf9ef-af79-1fa8-1ecf-c77004ea8177"><span><span id="docs-internal-guid-25110c4e-af78-f42f-a663-2cb79315b715"><span>RFC 2101 – IPv4 Address Behaviour Today</span></span></span></span></td> <td style="text-align: center;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-cfec7928-af75-0dc2-5c29-cb4ebc49de49"><span>IETF</span></span></td> <td><span id="docs-internal-guid-dd0e9bae-af72-9fcd-774d-865fb2dcf95a"><a href="https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2101"><span>https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2101</span></a></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td> <span id="docs-internal-guid-187bf9ef-af79-1fa8-1ecf-c77004ea8177"><span>RFC 2401 - Security Architecture for the Internet Protocol</span></span></td> <td style="text-align: center;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-cfec7928-af75-0dc2-5c29-cb4ebc49de49"><span>IETF</span></span></td> <td><span id="docs-internal-guid-bc2aeab4-af72-d558-94a5-654ef972384f"><a href="https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4301"><span>https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4301</span></a></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td><span>RFC 2663 – IP Network Address Translator (NAT) Terminology and Considerations</span></td> <td style="text-align: center;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-cfec7928-af75-0dc2-5c29-cb4ebc49de49"><span>IETF</span></span></td> <td><span id="docs-internal-guid-bdab6470-af73-0fc2-fdf9-9799ebf94915"><a href="https://tools.ietf.org/h